<br>
Usually one full dmg SoS will make sure you get full xp for the mobs.<br>
<br>
They hit fast and often, but not very hard. Aggro radius is small, so pet will only have to face max of 2 at a time. If you have the focused fire pet, you won't have to heal as much either.<br>
<br>
Fantastic xp/hr for lvl 29,30,31 diminishing returns after that. But be ready to play gems, long time between spawns (about 15 min).<br>
<br>
Check the post in the specific levelling section for more detail.<br>
<br>
Its a great spot on Stormhammer, I've never seen anyone else there. It may be more popular on the standard servers though....<br>
